The goal of a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">rent-</ENAMEX>regulation compromise should
be to diminish unfairness and mitigate perverse side effects without giving a
shock to the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">city</ENAMEX>'s social system. This argues for a fairly straightforward
