<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">apartments</ENAMEX>, which <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Gov.</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">George Pataki</ENAMEX> favors, perhaps on the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Republican</ENAMEX>
